"2. Starting near the top, use a knife பெறுநர் வெட்டு a மரம் curl. Slice down பெறுநர் the காரம் of the stick, but don't வெட்டு it off.\n"
"3. Repeat this process, but வெட்டு along the ridge உருவாக்கப்பட்டது by your last cut. Be careful not பெறுநர் வெட்டு அணை the previous curls.\n"
"4. Gather any curls that fell off.\n"
"5. பெறுநர் தொடங்கு a fire, follow the அடுத்தது பிரிவு using the feather stick அச் your tinder bundle.\n"
"\n"
"![](file:///android_asset/survival_guide/feather_stick.webp)\n"
"\n"
"## Starting a fire\n"
"<!-- K: start, light, ignite, matches, lighters, steel, ferro, ferrocerium, magnesium, flint, bow-drill, hand-drill, drill, magnifying, lens, tepee, structure -->\n"
"<!-- S: If you have a fire starter, use it. You can improvise if required, but it will be more difficult and requires practice. -->\n"
"\n"
"Once you have a site prepared and a sufficient அளிப்பு of tinder, kindling, and fuel, you அரே ready பெறுநர் தொடங்கு the fire. அச் you அரே building மேலே the fire, be careful not பெறுநர் smother the fire by எப்போதும் leaving a பிரிவு with an திற flame exposed. Also, avoid adding damp or பச்சை மரம் until your fire is hot and burning fuel.\n"
"\n"
"Here அரே the படிகள் you can follow பெறுநர் get it going:\n"
"\n"
"1. Place the tinder into a small bundle or nest on the ground.\n"
"2. Lean a few pieces of kindling against the tinder in a tepee shape.\n"
"3. Light the tinder.\n"
"4. Carefully கூட்டு kindling பெறுநர் the fire and blow into it பெறுநர் encourage growth.\n"
"5. Once your fire is steady, கூட்டு எரிபொருள் while maintaining a tepee structure.\n"
"\n"
"**Note**: When blowing into a fire, be gentle and take breaths away இருந்து the smoke.\n"
"\n"
"### Nursing an ember\n"
"An ember is a small piece of tinder that is burning but has not formed a flame. Once you have an ember, gently blow into it and தீவனம் it more tinder until a flame appears. Sometimes, it is easier பெறுநர் hold the tinder containing an ember and cup your hands closer together பெறுநர் கண்டுபிடி the வலது balance of உயிரகம், உயிர்வளி and fuel.\n"
"\n"
"### Firestarters\n"
"\n"
"- **Matches/lighters**: எப்போதும் have waterproof matches or a reliable lighter in your kit. These அரே the easiest முறைகள் பெறுநர் தொடங்கு a fire: just put the flame பெறுநர் the tinder.\n"
"- **Fire steel**: Durable and works in அனைத்தும் weather conditions, producing sparks பெறுநர் ignite your tinder. Scrape it quickly with the பின் of a knife or scraper பெறுநர் create sparks. க்கு best results, முள் the fire steel against the tinder and ground and scrape the steel towards the tinder. Some fire steel comes with a வெளிமம் block, which you can scrape அணை shavings into the tinder before striking பெறுநர் உதவி catch a spark.\n"
"- **Magnifying glass/lens**: குவி sunlight through a lens onto tinder பெறுநர் create an ember. A magnifying glass, prescription glasses, a fresnel lens, or இரட்டை a clear bottle filled with water can work. This சி-வைகாசி take a while, and direct sunlight is required.\n"
"\n"
"![](file:///android_asset/survival_guide/61.webp)\n"
"\n"
"The following முறைகள் அரே more challenging பெறுநர் create a fire with and require practice. If you கண்டுபிடி yourself here, it சி-வைகாசி be best பெறுநர் குவி on insulation and shelter பெறுநர் stay warm.\n"
"\n"
"- **Flint and steel**: Strike a flint rock with a steel கருவி பெறுநர் create sparks. The tinder must be very dry and delicate.\n"
"- **Bow drill**: Create உராய்வு by spinning a stick (drill) on a wooden காரம் (fireboard) using a bow பெறுநர் rotate the drill.\n"
"- **Hand drill**: Create உராய்வு by spinning a stick (drill) between your hands on a wooden காரம் (fireboard). இடு downward அழுத்தம் while spinning.\n"
"\n"
"### Using a bow drill\n"
"1. கண்டுபிடி a small, கிடைவளைவு stone or piece of hardwood with a small மனச்சோர்வு near the center பெறுநர் create the socket.\n"
"2. Create the drill by finding a straight, dry stick பற்றி 10-12 inches long and ¾ inch in diameter.\n"
"3. கண்டுபிடி a flat, dry piece of softwood க்கு the fireboard. Yucca, tamarack, aspen, balsam fir, basswood, poplar, cypress, cottonwood, alder, சிவப்பு cedar, and willow அரே preferred. Avoid resinous woods like pine.\n"
"4. Carve a slight மனச்சோர்வு பற்றி ½ பெறுநர் ¾ inch இருந்து the edge of the fireboard.\n"
"5. On the underside of the fireboard, make a V-shaped வெட்டு இருந்து the board's edge பெறுநர் the depression.\n"
"6. கண்டுபிடி a curved stick that can be used க்கு the bow. It should be பற்றி 12-14 inches long and ½ inch in diameter.\n"
"7. Attach a cord or shoelace பெறுநர் both ends of the bow.\n"
"8. கண்டுபிடி the fire pan, a கிடைவளைவு piece of bark or மரம் பெறுநர் catch the ember.\n"
"9. Wrap the drill into the bowstring so that it can உருளம் அச் it moves along the string.\n"
"10. Place the fireboard on மேலே of the fire pan so the V-shaped is touching.\n"
"11. Place the drill (attached பெறுநர் the bow) into the மனச்சோர்வு you carved into the fireboard.\n"
"12. Place the மனச்சோர்வு in the மாட்டி onto the மேலே end of the drill and இடு downward அழுத்தம் with your non-dominant hand.\n"
"13. Place your foot onto the fireboard (on the same பக்கம் அச் your non-dominant hand) and rest the hand holding the மாட்டி onto your knee.\n"
"14. With your dominant hand, move the bow பக்கம் பெறுநர் பக்கம் பெறுநர் cause the drill பெறுநர் spin. Be sure பெறுநர் go the entire length of the bow string. Keep a steady, fast pace.\n"
"15. You will தொடங்கு பெறுநர் see smoke after a while. Keep going until you அரே sure an ember has been created.\n"
"16. The ember should be transferred onto the fire pan (it சி-வைகாசி already be there) and moved பெறுநர் a tinder bundle where you can nurse it into a fire.\n"
"\n"
"![](file:///android_asset/survival_guide/64.webp)\n"
"\n"
"If you அரே using a hand drill, follow the same படிகள் அச் the bow drill, except don't create the bow and socket. Instead, உருளம் the drill between your palms until you reach the bottom, then தொடங்கு again இருந்து the top.\n"
"\n"
"## Extinguishing a fire\n"
"<!-- K: extinguish, safety -->\n"
"<!-- S: Thoroughly extinguish your fire with water or dirt. -->\n"
"\n"
"You should எப்போதும் have a plan பெறுநர் quickly extinguish your fire in case it begins பெறுநர் spread. Thoroughly extinguish your fire by dousing it with water or covering it with dirt. Make sure இல்லை embers remain that could reignite or cause a wildfire. If you அரே on a beach, do not cover the fire with sand; it can insulate the heat and cause burns.\n"
"\n"
"## Increasing warmth\n"
"<!-- K: rock, reflector, hand-warmer -->\n"
"<!-- S: Thoroughly extinguish your fire with water or dirt. -->\n"
"\n"
"To maximize the heat இருந்து your fire, you can கூட்டு more dry fuel, உருவாக்கு a fire reflector, heat மேலே rocks, or increase the insulation of your clothing and shelter.\n"
"\n"
"### Fire reflector\n"
"A fire reflector is a wall built behind the fire பெறுநர் reflect heat towards you and protect the fire இருந்து wind. Use rocks, logs, or பனி பெறுநர் create a barrier.\n"
"\n"
"![](file:///android_asset/survival_guide/56.webp)\n"
"\n"
"### Heating rocks\n"
"\n"
"You can also heat rocks **near** the fire and place them in your shelter or sleeping area. பெறுநர் avoid burns or fires, don't let the rocks get too hot; they should be warm பெறுநர் the touch. Be sure பெறுநர் சரிபார் how hot the stones அரே before touching them. Do not use rocks found near water sources, அச் they can explode in a fire. Alternatively, you could heat water and place it in a சரக்குப் பெட்டகம் or bottle பெறுநர் keep you warm.\n"
"\n"
"## Craft: charcoal\n"
"<!-- K: charcoal, filter, coal, craft -->\n"
"<!-- S: You can make charcoal by not allowing மரம் பெறுநர் burn fully. -->\n"
"\n"
"Charcoal is made by preventing மரம் இருந்து completely burning. It can be used க்கு filtering water, medicine, and அச் எரிபொருள் க்கு fires. You can grind charcoal into powder by placing it in a சரக்குப் பெட்டகம் and crushing it with a stick or rock.\n"
"\n"
"**Resources**\n"
"- Wood\n"
"- Water or dirt\n"
"\n"
"**Instructions**\n"
"1. Burn a fire down பெறுநர் coals.\n"
"2. Douse the fire with water or dirt பெறுநர் quickly extinguish it.\n"
"3. Wait க்கு the coals பெறுநர் cool; some charcoal should be among the ashes. Charcoal is very light and entirely black."

