"- **Watch method**: புள்ளியம் the hour hand of an analog watch at the sun; தெற்கு is roughly halfway between the hour hand and 12 o'clock in the வடக்கு Hemisphere. In the தெற்கு Hemisphere, புள்ளியம் the 12 o'clock position at the sun. If on daylight saving time, use 1 o'clock instead of 12.\n"
