"\n"
"## Planning a trip\n"
"<!-- K: plan, trip -->\n"
"<!-- S: Research the terrain, weather, and wildlife before leaving. Plan a route on a map and bring the necessary supplies. பங்கு this plan with someone you trust. -->\n"
"\n"
"Before going into the wilderness, have a plan that you can stick to. Research the terrain, weather conditions, wildlife, and plants you might encounter. சரிபார் local regulations and any permits you சி-வைகாசி need. Use an up-to-date map பெறுநர் plan your route and some alternative routes if the trails அரே impassable. Also, look மேலே trail conditions and the weather forecast க்கு your trip.\n"
"\n"
"Once you have a trip planned out, pack the necessary பற்சக்கரம் and supplies and சரிபார் அனைத்தும் of it பெறுநர் ensure it is functional. You should பங்கு your plan with a trusted person, which includes the routes, who you அரே going with, when you will be back, and when you will தொடர்பு them. If you don't have someone பெறுநர் whom you can tell these plans, leave a குறிப்பு with this செய்தி in a very visible place in your home. While you அரே hiking, stick பெறுநர் your route and avoid unnecessary risks.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## Signaling க்கு help\n"
"<!-- K: signal, help, contact, call, text, phone, whistle, mirror, smoke, flare, flashlight, ground-to-air -->\n"
"<!-- S: Try your கலன் phone; it சி-வைகாசி be able பெறுநர் make emergency calls. Otherwise, use a whistle, குறிகை mirror, smoke, flares, flashlight, or ground-to-air signals பெறுநர் attract attention. -->\n"
"\n"
"Signaling க்கு உதவி will increase your odds of being found. You should do this often, இரட்டை if you don't think anyone is nearby or can hear you.\n"
"\n"
"### கலன் phone\n"
"Many phones can call emergency சேவைகள் இரட்டை without a குறிகை இருந்து your carrier. If you can't make a call, try sending a உரை message. சரிபார் your phone periodically பெறுநர் see if you have a signal, but otherwise, keep it அணை or in airplane பயன்முறை பெறுநர் conserve battery. You சி-வைகாசி get a better குறிகை by moving பெறுநர் higher ground or an திற area.\n"
