"### Whistle\n"
"Three குறுக்கு blasts அரே the universal குறிகை க்கு help. You சி-வைகாசி want பெறுநர் cover your ears when using the whistle at full volume.\n"
"\n"
"### குறிகை mirror\n"
"Hold the mirror with one hand and extend your மற்றொன்று கை in front of you with your fingers in a V-shape and the target between your fingers. Reflect sunlight onto your fingers and slowly move the mirror மேலே and down பெறுநர் flash sunlight at the potential rescuers. You can use a phone screen அச் a குறிகை mirror, but it will be nowhere near அச் effective அச் an actual mirror and should be combined with another signal, such அச் smoke or a ground-to-air signal.\n"
"\n"
