"\n"
"### Flares\n"
"Flares அரே best seen at night or in low-visibility conditions. Follow the instructions on the flare பொதியாக்கம் and be aware of any legal restrictions on their use.\n"
"\n"
"### Flashlight\n"
"At night, a flashlight can be used பெறுநர் குறிகை க்கு help. Use the international distress signal, SOS, which is three குறுக்கு flashes, three long flashes, and three குறுக்கு flashes. If you don't remember the SOS signal, flash the light repeatedly in groups of three. Aim it in the direction of வானூர்தி or மற்றொன்று potential rescuers.\n"
"\n"
"### Ground-to-air signals\n"
"Ground-to-air signals அரே large markers you create on the ground பெறுநர் communicate with aircraft. Use rocks, logs, or மற்றொன்று materials பெறுநர் create a large \"V\" (means you require assistance) or an \"ஃச்\" (means you require medical assistance). Use contrasting or artificial colors பெறுநர் make the குறிகை more visible.\n"
"\n"
